    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161620/extras/438b3da4fa0ec53f0b88a3889d75d27c.avif?t=1710436253\" width=616 height=150 /></span><br><br>经历了长达五百年的和平之后，Antala再次笼罩在危险之中。Imë，你是新王国的守护者<strong>Lysfanga</strong>，王国的命运就掌握在你的手中。一座座尘封已久的古城重见天日，上古邪恶势力逃之夭夭，王国的安宁岌岌可危。 <br><br>但你并非孤军奋战。时间女神亲手赐予你<strong>时间神力</strong>，你可以在<strong>战斗中让时间倒流</strong>，召唤<strong>自己旧时本体的克隆体</strong>协助战斗，这是其他Lysfanga不曾拥有过的能力。只要熟练掌握这种神力，你自己就能成为一支军队，碾碎那群出逃的恶魔<strong>Raxes</strong>。<br><br>带领你的<strong>旧时本体大军</strong>一路攻城拔寨，扩充武器库，学习新法术。前路艰险，还望做好万全准备……<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >集结克隆大军</h2>发动Imë的神力“时空残响”后，可将时间倒流数秒并召唤自己的克隆体，集结大军击溃敌人。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161620/extras/50e8148df952d2d5b0b15290528147eb.poster.avif?t=1710436253\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161620/extras/50e8148df952d2d5b0b15290528147eb.webm?t=1710436253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161620/extras/50e8148df952d2d5b0b15290528147eb.mp4?t=1710436253\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >突破极限</h2>挑战自己的技能和谋略，实现自我超越。精进不休，反复挑战各个竞技场，刷新自己的最好成绩。敢于挑战自我，选择不同难度，修正战斗参数，解锁新的奖励。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >定制战斗</h2>每个竞技场都有无数通关方式。调整策略，用尽一切能用的手段，夺取胜利的荣光。善用“时空残响”、法术和武器，你将百战不殆。  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161620/extras/aed53f3e97cd5cbe6d0ef8ad0a97bd61.poster.avif?t=1710436253\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161620/extras/aed53f3e97cd5cbe6d0ef8ad0a97bd61.webm?t=1710436253\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探访上古巨城</h2>旧时的枷锁已然消散。Raxes重获自由，再次掀起混乱。探索上古大陆曾封印在时间中的废弃古城，揭晓Raxes再度现世的真相。",
